snippet.title: DESCENSION Official Trailer - Retro Quake-like FPS made in Unity
snippet.description:
[Free Download Link] https://sodaraptor.itch.io/descension
Trailer for a game I've just wrapped up development on this past week with a group of friends. I did the art! If you grew up playing games like Quake, Doom, or Unreal Tournament, you'll like Descension
